<p>Medicines can sometimes cause a problem when taken alone or with other drugs. This is called an adverse reaction. Find out if the medicine you are taking has a history of adverse reactions.</p><p><strong>Enter the name of one or two drugs to find out if any adverse reactions were reported.</strong></p><form action="/" method="post" class="form-inline drug-submittal">  <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{{ csrf_token() }}}" />  <div class="form-group drug-entry">    <label for="drugOne" class="sr-only">Drug 1</label>    <input type="text" class="form-control drug-one" name="drugOne" value="{{ $drugOne or '' }}" placeholder="Drug 1">    <label for="drugTwo" class="sr-only">Drug 2 (optional)</label>    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="drugTwo" value="{{ $drugTwo or '' }}" placeholder="Drug 2 (optional)">  </div>  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-primary">SEARCH</button></form>